    "For whitespace triggers, we utilize \"\\r\", \"\\f\", and \"\\v\", while for punctuation triggers, we employe \"|\", \"~\", and \">\".",
    "Evaluations using the Mistral and Gemma models demonstrate the effectiveness of these triggers, as shown in the Table 13.",
    "We select state-of-the-art language models with diverse architectures to evaluate the generalizability of SHIP.",
